 /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c89b15b917002ee2cb8fb73490a4aafe81b6db","tid":2112554,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T03:56:04.000Z","msg":"CCTVB罔顧人命 無懼武肺"},{"pid":"59abb8327ddba85475ad865cb926fb9e6b59d75a","tid":2112554,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"686d8f094ce9e814e95310e7902ff7f4c345d2b7","tid":2112554,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T11:42:38.000Z","msg":"《2020香港小姐》早前經過兩輪網上及傳媒記招，正式選出16名入圍的佳麗，現時候選佳麗主要屬香港區，海外佳麗是否有入圍者有待公布，而不少佳麗亦向傳媒表示正式辭去本身工作，專心參加選美，齊齊挑戰TVB形容的港姐絕世筍工。<br />\n<br />\n《2020香港小姐競選》選出16位香港入圍佳麗，包括：侯嘉欣、何孟珊、麥詩晴、范倩雯、陳楨怡、源菲然、廖慧儀、郭柏妍、梁懿婷、謝恩靈、賴琦媛、連佳麗、黃婉恩、羅雪妍、陳煦凝、鄺美璇。<br />\n<br />\n日前16位佳麗已赴TVB進行閉門活動，而今晚（7月17日）則會再度進行網上面試。<br />\n<br />\n今年TVB港姐以「疫市筍工」為口號，據知不少入圍佳麗亦響應號召，當知道入圍後已正式辭工，全力做好選美準備。<br />\n<br />\n仲要之後有5個海外嘅會隔離14日參加決賽,CCTVB似乎好想有人武肺死係電視城到喎<br />\n============================================<br />\n如果想準時收到TVB任務，一定要響Facebook同Telegram follow sayno4tvb團隊（我唔係佢地團隊），又或者<strong><span class=\"red\">得閒click入呢個Post（<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2059659\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2059659</a>）我會盡量每日更新</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno4tvb%2F&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=824e19cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/</a><br />\nTG: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno4tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno4tvb&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=b44f5627\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno4tvb</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NbYiswE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt